  "description": "A writer with a large following posts a thread about structural racism. The thread is carefully sourced, emotionally calibrated, and formatted for maximum engagement. It receives thousands of shares. The writer gains followers, credibility, and a sense of having done meaningful work. The structural racism the thread describes continues unaltered. The writer writes another thread.",
